{"tid":592762,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好想係到多謝啱啱968上層嗰位姐姐","createTime":"2018-03-14T12:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T15:10:56.000Z","uid":56096,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f4d6a4eeea5189782564eac3eacd59c6bed940fa","tid":592762,"uid":56096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T12:59:29.000Z","msg":"話說小弟係銅鑼灣拎完嘢之後搭車返屋企 上巴士嗰陣完全冇為意到個手抽紙袋大大 上到上層坐低咗先知出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  嗰袋太大 放地下都佔咗隔離位三分一 (即係食咗隔離三分一放腳位) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係架車已經開始多人 我打消咗落返下層嘅念頭 放個紙袋係地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  中途有幾個男人 一坐低咗就彈返起身坐其他位 好似搞到我有傳染病咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我勁尷尬 成個身緊張到好熱血沸騰㷫烚烚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  跟住有個姐姐坐低咗 我見到佢冇起身嘅意欲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 於是我即刻同佢講 &ldquo;唔好意思啊 踼到都無所謂 冇為意到個袋太大個&rdquo; <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟住個姐姐好好人咁答 &ldquo;唔緊要啊 阻唔到我&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 類似啲咁嘅嘢 我聽唔清楚因為我尷尬到唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n之後個姐姐就係大㰖落咗車轉車 本身諗住係佢落車嗰陣多謝佢 不過唔夠膽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   多謝你啊!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dd774afefa35c8359e3dbd4924d23eafaeb981e","tid":592762,"uid":54359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T13:42:20.000Z","msg":"姐姐其實想走，不過架車開始多人走唔到<br />\n到大欖一有機會就即閃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea33384f7c9744e129e59b18305487a287f575f","tid":592762,"uid":32470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T13:47:17.000Z","msg":"咁易動情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7774e36ad3232b0eaec07f48262149f013c033","tid":592762,"uid":56096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dd774afefa35c8359e3dbd4924d23eafaeb981e","tid":592762,"uid":54359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T13:42:20.000Z","msg":"姐姐其實想走，不過架車開始多人走唔到<br />\n到大欖一有機會就即閃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T14:46:02.000Z","msg":"唔想你咁樣破壞佢形象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d7793a6c12afb77c0c2a6f7304759ddb79935f","tid":592762,"uid":56096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ea33384f7c9744e129e59b18305487a287f575f","tid":592762,"uid":32470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T13:47:17.000Z","msg":"咁易動情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T14:46:13.000Z","msg":"我只係想多謝佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c66cd65aa0eda87097a512e0b84a45a0cbd76c4f","tid":592762,"uid":56096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dd774afefa35c8359e3dbd4924d23eafaeb981e","tid":592762,"uid":54359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T13:42:20.